txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Huge goo from the insects and spiders from the lands surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'We will ensure that this is used to help our people. Thank you.'
'The goo that comes from the insects and spiders can be useful in many ways. We would like some collected for us.'
Council of the North Task: Huge Goo
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of huge goo to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the huge goo to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver huge goo from insects and spiders surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Huge goo from the insects and spiders from the lands surrounding Aughaire.
